### Health
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

###
# ── PROJECTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List projects (expect seed project "GTD 入门项目")
GET http://localhost:3001/api/projects

### Create project
POST http://localhost:3001/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "新项目",
  "description": "REST Client 测试",
  "color": "#e03e3e"
}

### Update project (replace {{project_id}} with id from Create response)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/projects/{{project_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "更新后的项目名", "color": "#10b981" }

### Archive project (soft-delete: sets archived=1)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/projects/{{project_id}}

###
# ── TASKS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all tasks (sorted by sort_order)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/tasks

### Filter by status
GET http://localhost:3001/api/tasks?status=planned

### Filter by project
GET http://localhost:3001/api/tasks?project_id={{seed_project_id}}

### Create task (sort_order auto-computed as last+1 in the column)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "API 测试任务",
  "status": "planned",
  "estimated_pomodoros": 2,
  "project_id": "{{seed_project_id}}"
}

### Move task to in_progress
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/tasks/{{task_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "in_progress" }

### Move task to done (completedAt auto-filled)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/tasks/{{task_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "done" }

### Update sort_order (drag-drop: client computes midpoint, sends new value)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/tasks/{{task_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "sort_order": 1.5 }

### Delete task (hard delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/tasks/{{task_id}}

###
# ── POMODOROS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Start pomodoro
POST http://localhost:3001/api/pomodoros
Content-Type: application/json

{ "task_id": "{{in_progress_task_id}}", "duration_seconds": 1500 }

### Complete pomodoro (atomic: status=completed + task.completed_pomodoros += 1)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/pomodoros/{{pom_id}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{ "notes": "专注完成，无干扰" }

### Interrupt pomodoro (status=interrupted, does NOT increment counter)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/pomodoros/{{pom_id}}/interrupt
Content-Type: application/json

{ "notes": "被电话打断" }

### Today's completed pomodoros
GET http://localhost:3001/api/pomodoros/today

### Task history
GET http://localhost:3001/api/pomodoros?task_id={{task_id}}

###
# ── CALENDAR ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Today's window
### today_start = midnight ms timestamp, today_end = today_start + 86400000
GET http://localhost:3001/api/calendar?start={{today_start_ms}}&end={{today_end_ms}}

### Validation: missing params → 400
GET http://localhost:3001/api/calendar
